2026-05-14T06:58:58.1905091Z 21    <!--
2026-05-14T06:58:58.1905472Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T06:58:58.1905668Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T06:58:58.1906015Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T06:58:58.1906333Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T06:58:58.1906660Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T06:58:58.1906971Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
